Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,西藏蝮蛇毒\N{\b0\fs12}Tibetan pit viper venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,常用劑量對你來說沒用  對吧\N{\b0\fs12}A constant dose of that can't be good for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他會像當初斯萊德那樣昏迷\N{\b0\fs12}It'll keep him sedated like it did Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒提到伊莎貝爾•羅切夫的死嗎\N{\b0\fs12}No mention on Isabel Rochev's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-殺我吧  殺我吧  -不  不\N{\b0\fs12}- Choose. Choose! - No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不  媽  你幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}No, mom! Mom, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要殺我的孩子\N{\b0\fs12}Both my children will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你擁有真正的勇氣\N{\b0\fs12}You possess true courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事結束之前  還有一個人\N{\b0\fs12}There is still one person who has to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,必須得死\N{\b0\fs12}before this can end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要  -媽\N{\b0\fs12}- No... - Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我莊嚴宣誓\N{\b0\fs12}I do solemnly swear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我會支援\N{\b0\fs12}that I will support,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,維護和遵守星城憲章\N{\b0\fs12}defend, and abide by the Starling City charter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我會忠誠地\N{\b0\fs12}And that I will faithfully
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,接受星城市長\N{\b0\fs12}discharge the duties of the office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,辦公室的職責\N{\b0\fs12}of mayor of Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我會代表星城居民\N{\b0\fs12}That I will tirelessly pursue justice on behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不屈不撓地追尋正義\N{\b0\fs12}of all of Starling's citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,公正無私\N{\b0\fs12}impartially,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,盡我最大的能力\N{\b0\fs12}to the best of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,願上帝助我\N{\b0\fs12}So help me god.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我陪著你呢\N{\b0\fs12}I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩女士\N{\b0\fs12}Ms. Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對你的損失  我深表遺憾\N{\b0\fs12}I wanted to offer my sincere condolences on your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽是個好人\N{\b0\fs12}Your mother was a good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她會是個很棒的市長\N{\b0\fs12}She would have made a wonderful mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和奧利弗談談\N{\b0\fs12}I'd love to speak with Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你看見了他\N{\b0\fs12}Well, if you see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴他  他錯過了自己母親的葬禮\N{\b0\fs12}tell him he missed his own mother's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好幾天都沒人看見奧利弗了\N{\b0\fs12}No one's seen Oliver for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們應對悲傷的方式各有不同\N{\b0\fs12}We all deal with grief in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,失去母親簡直...\N{\b0\fs12}And the loss of a parent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它能改變你\N{\b0\fs12}Well, it changes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你意識到你的祖先現在都指望著你\N{\b0\fs12}When you realize that your ancestors now look to you;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,繼承家族的遺產  延續他們的傳奇\N{\b0\fs12}That your family's legacy, their continuing works,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠你一個人了\N{\b0\fs12}are solely in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你看見奧利弗  告訴他我來過了\N{\b0\fs12}If you see Oliver, please tell him that I came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\b0\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我為什麼要哭\N{\b0\fs12}I don't even know why I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不喜歡莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't even like Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,別人剛死就這樣說她  真是不好\N{\b0\fs12}Terrible thing to say about someone after they've just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,容我辯護一句  她人可不好\N{\b0\fs12}In my defense, she was not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她很惡毒\N{\b0\fs12}She was diabolical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這個詞在別人的葬禮上不常聽到\N{\b0\fs12}Not a word you often hear at someone's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是為她哭泣  費利西蒂  而是為奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}U're not crying for her, Felicity, you're crying for Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎麼能不在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}How could he not be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果奧利弗夠聰明\N{\b0\fs12}If Oliver's smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就會跑去他的島上躲起來\N{\b0\fs12}He ran back to his island to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但也許他會出席你們的葬禮\N{\b0\fs12}But maybe he'll attend your funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很喜歡這張照片\N{\b0\fs12}I always loved this photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你媽媽看起來特別漂亮\N{\b0\fs12}I thought your mother looked particularly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她不覺得\N{\b0\fs12}Well, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她覺得看起來像是暴眼\N{\b0\fs12}She thought she looked bug-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒說過\N{\b0\fs12}She never said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你現在怎麼樣  -很不好\N{\b0\fs12}- How are you holding up? - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽為了你付出了生命  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Your mother gave her life for you, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她向你展示了有多愛你\N{\b0\fs12}She showed you how much she loved you in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有父母能做到這樣\N{\b0\fs12}very few parents ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她死的時候都覺得我恨她\N{\b0\fs12}She died thinking I hated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們需要的只是真相\N{\b0\fs12}But all we ever needed was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死她的是一個謊言\N{\b0\fs12}It was a lie that killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\b0\fs12}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,之前他和奧利弗都在那座小島上\N{\b0\fs12}He was on that island with Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,出於某種原因  他憎恨奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}And despises him for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的生活中有個精神病\N{\b0\fs12}There was a psychopath in our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而我哥哥從來沒警告過我們\N{\b0\fs12}and my brother never warned us about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  你哥哥愛你勝過自己的生命\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, your brother loves you more than life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你該留著那張照片\N{\b0\fs12}You should keep that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這個潛水艇有六十多年了\N{\b0\fs12}This sub is over 60 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,戰時這艇擱淺  米拉庫魯就在這艇上\N{\b0\fs12}It was carrying the Mirakuru during the war when it ran aground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有血\N{\b0\fs12}Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德的\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他流血過多  即將死去\N{\b0\fs12}He was bleeding out, dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,於是我們決定給他注射米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}Until we decided to give him the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你這主意不怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}Not one of your better ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓你修好潛水艇這個主意怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}What about my idea for you to fix this sub?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-你當過海軍  -是俄國海軍\N{\b0\fs12}- You were in the navy. - The Russian navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們教我們如何擊沉日本潛水艇  而不是駕駛\N{\b0\fs12}They taught us how to sink Japanese sub, not pilot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,阿納托利  拜託\N{\b0\fs12}Anatoly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道機會渺茫  但如果我們能開動潛水艇\N{\b0\fs12}I know it's a long shot, but if we get this sub operational,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就能擊敗斯萊德  毀掉米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}we can blow Slade and the Mirakuru out of the water
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然後離開這座小島\N{\b0\fs12}and get the hell off of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你有更好的主意\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, unless you have a better idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們回家的唯一機會\N{\b0\fs12}this is our only chance of getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我盡量\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊那晚過後  沒人見過斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}No one has seen Slade Wilson since the night of the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有再威脅奎恩家族\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, he hasn't made any further threats on the Queen family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們得找到這個王八...\N{\b0\fs12}but we got to find this son of a--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,先失陪了\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,追悼會沒見到你\N{\b0\fs12}Missed you at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我得回來\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. I had to get back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-看看案子怎麼樣了  -有線索了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}- see what was happening with the case. - Any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  威爾遜簡直是個幽靈\N{\b0\fs12}No. Wilson's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是唯一失蹤的人\N{\b0\fs12}He's not the only one who's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹有聯繫過你嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You heard from your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她只給我發了一條短信  說要換個環境\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing apart from a text that she needed a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你還有什麼心事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Something else on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德\N{\b0\fs12}It's Sebastian Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得有點不對勁\N{\b0\fs12}There's something that doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-勞蕾爾  -爸爸  我知道你在想什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- Laurel... - Dad, I know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我指控他殺了他父親的時候  我太急躁\N{\b0\fs12}When I accused him of killing his father, I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有過失誤\N{\b0\fs12}But just because I had a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,並不意味著塞巴斯蒂安的事我就錯了\N{\b0\fs12}doesn't mean I was wrong about Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,請你不要糾結這事了好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Please, don't go down this road again, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼又提起這個了\N{\b0\fs12}What's bringing this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在追悼會上看到他了\N{\b0\fs12}I saw him at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我想到他當選市長的唯一原因是\N{\b0\fs12}And it struck me that the only reason that he's mayor now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,莫伊拉被殺了\N{\b0\fs12}is because Moira was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  被斯萊德•威爾遜殺的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, by Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這之間有聯繫呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if there's a connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾經對我說過\N{\b0\fs12}You once told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一個員警能做多好取決於直覺\N{\b0\fs12}a cop is only as good as his gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是員警的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I'm the daughter of a cop,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的直覺告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}and I know in my gut
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安不是你想的那種人\N{\b0\fs12}Sebastian is not the man that you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝  上一次\N{\b0\fs12}Baby, last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個醉鬼  你不相信我是對的\N{\b0\fs12}I was a drunk. And you were right not to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}But, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在需要你的信任\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to trust me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這項法律只是第一步\N{\b0\fs12}This legislation is the first step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,讓星城重拾昨日的光芒\N{\b0\fs12}toward making Starling City the jewel that it once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再次成為一顆明珠\N{\b0\fs12}The jewel that it can be again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有您的電話  布拉德市長\N{\b0\fs12}Phone call for you, Mayor Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我還在適應人們這麼叫我  阿莉莎\N{\b0\fs12}I'm still getting used to people calling me that, Alyssa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讓對方留言吧\N{\b0\fs12}Please take a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對方堅持要與您通話\N{\b0\fs12}The caller insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他是您父親\N{\b0\fs12}He said he's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能\N{\b0\fs12}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\b0\fs12}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我來接\N{\b0\fs12}I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  塞巴斯蒂安\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打攪你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想打個電話來\N{\b0\fs12}I just wanted to check in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,問問你第一天上任感覺如何\N{\b0\fs12}and see how your first day is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}Very well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我現在有點忙\N{\b0\fs12}But I'm a little busy right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不介意的話我過一會兒再打給你\N{\b0\fs12}So if you'll allow me to call you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡快的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll do that as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\b0\fs12}No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我確信你有很多事情要做\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sure you have quite a lot of business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟你現在是市長了\N{\b0\fs12}You are the mayor now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以開始工作吧\N{\b0\fs12}So get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的蛇毒所剩不多了\N{\b0\fs12}We're almost out of snake venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊這個樣子讓我想起了巴里\N{\b0\fs12}Seeing Roy like this reminds me of Barry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里又讓我想起了尖端科技研究實驗室\N{\b0\fs12}And Barry reminds me of S.T.A.R. Labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尖端科技研究實驗室讓我想起了\N{\b0\fs12}S.T.A.R. Labs reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他們正在研究的米拉庫魯的解藥\N{\b0\fs12}of the Mirakuru cure that they're working on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我們現在能用上多好呀\N{\b0\fs12}which we could really use...right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  特別是因為伊莎貝爾•羅切夫\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, especially since Isabel Rochev
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定被人注射了那玩意\N{\b0\fs12}was clearly injected with the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道\N{\b0\fs12}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因為除此之外\N{\b0\fs12}'cause there's no other way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她不可能被九毫米中空彈斃命後\N{\b0\fs12}she could be walking around after being shot dead-on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還能到處跑\N{\b0\fs12}with a nine-millimeter hollow point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我給奧利弗留了一大堆關於\N{\b0\fs12}I've left about a dozen messages for Oliver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾•羅切夫回歸的語音留言  但毫無回應\N{\b0\fs12}about Isabel being back. No response.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到他的線索了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You have any luck finding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很多  但全是壞消息\N{\b0\fs12}Tons. All of it bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,總之是他的護照  手機\N{\b0\fs12}There's been no activity on his passport, cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行帳戶  還有其他東西全都沒有活動\N{\b0\fs12}or bank accounts-- what's left of them, anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城第一銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,面部識別也未能在任何機場\N{\b0\fs12}And facial recognition hasn't spotted him in any airport,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,公交或火車站發現他\N{\b0\fs12}bus, or train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉呢\N{\b0\fs12}What about Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一樣毫無蹤跡\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格  一般來講人們不會消失得這麼徹底\N{\b0\fs12}Dig, people don't just go missing like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除非\N{\b0\fs12}unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼想  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Don't go there, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她真是那樣了呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果奧利弗那樣了呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if Oliver is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我們找不到他的原因是\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe the reason we can't find him is because--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}He's alive, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他死了  伊莎貝爾•羅切夫肯定\N{\b0\fs12}If he wasn't, Isabel Rochev wouldn't be so shy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,會毫不遮掩地告訴我們  相信我  他還活著\N{\b0\fs12}about rubbing it in our faces. Believe me, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你有其他辦法找到他\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I hope you have some way on how to find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我已經竭盡所能了\N{\b0\fs12}because I am running out of places to look and people to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道該去找誰\N{\b0\fs12}I know who to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你同意見我們\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for agreeing to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為上次碰面的時候已經說得很清楚\N{\b0\fs12}Thought I made it clear after our last meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,超能力聯合調查組不再對你提供幫助了\N{\b0\fs12}As far as A.R.G.U.S. is concerned, you're out of favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為我自己的事  阿曼達\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not asking for myself, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為星城的每一個人\N{\b0\fs12}I'm asking for everyone in Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你們找到奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to find Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那臺計算機用的是XK-15型處理器\N{\b0\fs12}That computer's running an XK-15 processor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那個東西應該還不存在才對\N{\b0\fs12}But that's not even supposed to exist yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要一個\N{\b0\fs12}I want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我你找到了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Let me know what you find.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒時間找你的朋友  狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}I don't have time to keep track of your friends, Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在處理更緊急的事\N{\b0\fs12}We deal with more pressing issues here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白  奧利弗失蹤了\N{\b0\fs12}You don't understand. Oliver's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也許他只是需要點時間\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe he needs some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你們兩人\N{\b0\fs12}Or is it possible that the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是沒有找對地方\N{\b0\fs12}simply haven't been looking in the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們試過面部識別了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did you try facial recognition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了  做過三遍了\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I ran it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達  拜託了\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜有一支\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson has an army
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,強大軍隊個個跟他一樣\N{\b0\fs12}of men just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少人曾經注射過米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}How many men have been exposed to the Mirakuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,足夠徹底破壞這座城市了\N{\b0\fs12}Enough to lay waste to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在就需要找到奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}We need to find Oliver right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡力的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-莎拉聯繫過你嗎  -沒有\N{\b0\fs12}- Have you heard from Sara? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-你能打電話問下曼蒂能不能看店嗎  -好的\N{\b0\fs12}- Can you just call Mandy and see if she'll cover our bar?  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾•羅切夫\N{\b0\fs12}Isabel Rochev.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是誰\N{\b0\fs12}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我能為你做什麼  羅切夫小姐\N{\b0\fs12}What can I do for you, Ms. Rochev?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,請節哀順變  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry for your loss, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你來就是為了這個嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that why you came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,向我表示哀悼\N{\b0\fs12}Offer me your condolences?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對  哀悼  還有這個\N{\b0\fs12}My condolences, and to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是讓你騰出酒吧的通知\N{\b0\fs12}It's a notice to vacate the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這個酒吧還有它所位於的鋼鐵廠\N{\b0\fs12}This club and the steel factory in which its located
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都是奎恩聯合企業的財產\N{\b0\fs12}are all assets of Queen Consolidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  你不能這樣  -事已成定局\N{\b0\fs12}- No, you--you can't do this. - It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有多長時間\N{\b0\fs12}How long do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,兩天\N{\b0\fs12}A couple days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,泰森議員想邀請你吃晚飯\N{\b0\fs12}Councilman Tyson is asking about dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚有安排了\N{\b0\fs12}I already have plans tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我不是故意要闖進來的\N{\b0\fs12}Hi. Excuse me, I didn't mean to barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只是前臺沒人  所以\N{\b0\fs12}It's just that nobody was at your front desk, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  沒事  請進\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, of course, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你先出去吧\N{\b0\fs12}Give us a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,兩天裡見到你兩次\N{\b0\fs12}Twice in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎有如此榮幸\N{\b0\fs12}To what do I owe the pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是希望是有好事\N{\b0\fs12}I wish I could say that this was pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有個案子要你幫忙\N{\b0\fs12}but it's about a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛上任  就開始有人找我幫忙了\N{\b0\fs12}I've barely moved in and people are already asking me for favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在真是市長了啊\N{\b0\fs12}I guess I really have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,的確如此\N{\b0\fs12}You certainly have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧  我能幫你什麼忙\N{\b0\fs12}So tell me, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,墨菲和鄧利維的案件\N{\b0\fs12}Murphy vs. Dunleavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,政府指控一家房地產開發商\N{\b0\fs12}The state's charged a real estate developer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說他們以所謂的"道德問題"為理由\N{\b0\fs12}for turning away low-income tenants
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拒絕低收入的租客\N{\b0\fs12}based on his so-called "Morality."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐吧  我猜啊\N{\b0\fs12}Have a seat. Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們親愛的公平租賃政策的長官\N{\b0\fs12}Our dear fair housing commissioner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不願意出庭當你的專家證人\N{\b0\fs12}isn't willing to testify as your expert witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  而且前任市長也不打算對他施壓\N{\b0\fs12}Exactly. And your predecessor wasn't willing to lean on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼你很幸運  因為我跟他不一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Well, lucky for you, I'm not my predecessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎  這事讓我想起了以前\N{\b0\fs12}You know, this actually reminds me of one I had
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我當社區組織者時接的一個案子\N{\b0\fs12}during my days as a community organizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我正希望如此\N{\b0\fs12}I was hoping that it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在創新聯合會見過很多這樣的案件\N{\b0\fs12}I've seen dozens of cases like this at CNRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都記得自己的出身  這是好事\N{\b0\fs12}Well, it's a good thing we both remember where we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我很樂意幫你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你能回地檢辦工作  我真的很高興\N{\b0\fs12}I'm really glad you got your job back at the DA's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待我們能長久一起共事\N{\b0\fs12}I look forward to us working together for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\b0\fs12}As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有用嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們馬上就要遠程訪問那臺電腦了\N{\b0\fs12}We're about to remote access the computer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說  如果你哪天律師當膩了\N{\b0\fs12}I'll tell you this, if you ever get tired of practicing law,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,去當間諜一定很成功\N{\b0\fs12}you'd make a pretty decent spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這事經過批準了對吧\N{\b0\fs12}You guys have a warrant for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你就...\N{\b0\fs12}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好極了\N{\b0\fs12}Terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,至少告訴我這是黑了誰的電腦吧\N{\b0\fs12}Could you at least tell me who's computer you bugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城  市長辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們開什麼玩笑  我還給他投過票呢\N{\b0\fs12}You're kidding. I voted for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要知道\N{\b0\fs12}I need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德有什麼見不得光的檔資料\N{\b0\fs12}if there's anything incriminating in Blood's files.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管了  反正這工作也沒什麼前途\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell, this is a dead end job, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去都沒問題\N{\b0\fs12}This all looks pretty benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很多政策性檔\N{\b0\fs12}Lots of policy papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從他競選辦公室轉過來的舊文件\N{\b0\fs12}old documents transferred from his campaign office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,新聞發布稿\N{\b0\fs12}Draft press releases...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  剛才那張\N{\b0\fs12}Wait, wait, wait, click back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,立即發布  "發生了這種悲劇\N{\b0\fs12}"For immediate release-- my thoughts and prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我在此為奎恩家族\N{\b0\fs12}are with the Queen family in the aftermath
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,誠心默哀祈禱"\N{\b0\fs12}of this unspeakable tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是在莫伊拉死後寫了新聞發言稿唄\N{\b0\fs12}So he worked up a press release after Moira was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的\N{\b0\fs12}No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在莫伊拉死前寫好的\N{\b0\fs12}He wrote that the day before Moira died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她說的沒錯  看這個落款的時間\N{\b0\fs12}She's right. Look at the timestamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}2014年4月23日  上午8:16
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安早就知道斯萊德會殺她\N{\b0\fs12}Sebastian knew Slade was going to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這是TX50衛星頻率通訊機嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that the satellite frequency communicator TX50?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以摸一下嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我承認這有點怪有點詭異\N{\b0\fs12}I know that sounds a little weird and creepy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我現實生活裡從來沒見過這個\N{\b0\fs12}but I've never seen one in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是機密設備  斯莫克小姐\N{\b0\fs12}It's classified equipment, Ms. Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定覺得很有權威\N{\b0\fs12}You must feel very powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道每個人的每件事\N{\b0\fs12}knowing everything about everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是像史達林那種邪惡獨裁者那樣\N{\b0\fs12}Not powerful in an evil dictator Stalin way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,更像是"知識就是力量"那樣\N{\b0\fs12}More of a... knowledge is power, way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,長官  有情況\N{\b0\fs12}Ma'am. We have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我早該想到\N{\b0\fs12}I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗在他部署行動的那個藏身處\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver's at the lair from which he conducts his operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們剛從那過來啊\N{\b0\fs12}But we were just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那個地方\N{\b0\fs12}Not that lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他另一個藏身之所\N{\b0\fs12}His other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就像騎自行車一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Like riding bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過在水下騎\N{\b0\fs12}Underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼聲音\N{\b0\fs12}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們被卡住了\N{\b0\fs12}We're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,正如當時的日本人那樣\N{\b0\fs12}Like Japanese were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,潛水艇都有魚雷的吧\N{\b0\fs12}Submarines have torpedoes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能炸開一條路出去嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can we blast our way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在明白為什麼說你們倆天生一對了\N{\b0\fs12}I can see why you two are made for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡用爆炸解決問題\N{\b0\fs12}You like your explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好  魚雷\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, torpedoes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我去[俄語]\N{\b0\fs12}Chert voz'mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是回轉魚雷\N{\b0\fs12}These are kaiten torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是人工作業的\N{\b0\fs12}Manually operated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,得有人從裡面控制魚雷\N{\b0\fs12}Someone needs to steer from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那控制的人怎麼躲開魚雷的爆炸\N{\b0\fs12}Okay, but then, how do they get away from the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒法躲開\N{\b0\fs12}They do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-你們怎麼找到我的  -沃勒說的\N{\b0\fs12}- How did you find me? - Waller.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都很擔心你\N{\b0\fs12}We were worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你連你媽的葬禮都沒參加\N{\b0\fs12}After you missed your mother's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我沒有去\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry that I didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時去墓地了\N{\b0\fs12}I left for the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可最後卻到這裡了\N{\b0\fs12}But I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是...\N{\b0\fs12}Here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是防止鋼鐵廠那邊出問題\N{\b0\fs12}Here was a secondary facility
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,才建造的備用設施\N{\b0\fs12}in case the foundry was compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻變成了一個我可以...\N{\b0\fs12}But it became somewhere that I could just go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,獨自待著的地方\N{\b0\fs12}be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她因我而死\N{\b0\fs12}She's dead because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前\N{\b0\fs12}Five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以治好斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}I could have cured Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那樣  這一切都不會發生\N{\b0\fs12}And that would have prevented all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而現在\N{\b0\fs12}And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下這些所有我關心的人\N{\b0\fs12}all the people left that I care about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都成了他的獵物\N{\b0\fs12}we are all in his crosshairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚一切都將結束\N{\b0\fs12}It ends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼結束\N{\b0\fs12}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我把自己交給斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}I turn myself over to Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要終結這場仇殺\N{\b0\fs12}I end this vendetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你以為把自己交給他\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, you think this ends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切就會結束了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}with you turning yourself over to Slade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她死了之後\N{\b0\fs12}After she was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他告訴我必須再死一個人\N{\b0\fs12}he told me that one more person had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就結束了\N{\b0\fs12}And then it would end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德殺了我就結束了\N{\b0\fs12}This ends for Slade when he kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不接受\N{\b0\fs12}I don't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不應該接受\N{\b0\fs12}You shouldn't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能這麼逆來順受  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}You can't just accept things, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我接受了自己的命運\N{\b0\fs12}If I had accepted my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就會像我母親一樣成為賭城的雞尾酒女郎\N{\b0\fs12}I would be a cocktail waitress in Vegas like my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我永遠也不會去上大學\N{\b0\fs12}and I never would have gone to college,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠也不會跑到千里之外\N{\b0\fs12}and I never would have moved a thousand miles away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在奎恩聯合企業工作\N{\b0\fs12}to work at Queen Consolidated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠也不會相信一個兜帽瘋子的話\N{\b0\fs12}and I never would have believed some crazy guy in a hood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他說我不僅僅能做一個技術女\N{\b0\fs12}when he told me I could be more than just some IT girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  不要這樣做\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有人曾經跟我說過\N{\b0\fs12}Someone once told me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄主義的本質就是為他人犧牲\N{\b0\fs12}that the essence of heroism is to die so others can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那麼簡單  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It's not that simple, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼簡單\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德的整個計劃\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's whole plan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是要奪走我的一切\N{\b0\fs12}was to take everything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他做到了\N{\b0\fs12}He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他贏了\N{\b0\fs12}He wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只要我死  就都結束了\N{\b0\fs12}All that's left is for me to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不  一定還有別的方法\N{\b0\fs12}No, there has to be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有了\N{\b0\fs12}There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  拜託  我明白你很難過\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, please. I understand you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們全都有點情緒化\N{\b0\fs12}This is an emotional time for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是鬧情緒\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not being emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我成了孤兒\N{\b0\fs12}I'm...I'm an orphan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個沒有工作沒有家的孤兒\N{\b0\fs12}I'm a jobless and homeless orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這兒什麼都沒有了\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing left for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我還在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  但是\N{\b0\fs12}I thank you for that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話  我需要重新開始\N{\b0\fs12}Honestly, I need to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒去參加葬禮\N{\b0\fs12}We missed you at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒參加追悼會\N{\b0\fs12}And the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我沒有出席\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry that I couldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡出什麼事了\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭在考慮要離開星城\N{\b0\fs12}Thea's thinking of leaving Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在考慮  我決定了\N{\b0\fs12}No, I am leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特  能讓我跟我妹妹聊幾句嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Walter, could I speak to my sister for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你運氣更好\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sure you'll have better luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  拜託  別想要說服我留下來\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, please. Just don't even try to convince me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會的  我覺得離開是個好主意\N{\b0\fs12}I won't. I think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該盡可能遠離星城\N{\b0\fs12}You should get as far from Starling City as you possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一家人\N{\b0\fs12}In our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在你  我  媽媽還有爸爸之間\N{\b0\fs12}out of you, me, mom and dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最好的那個\N{\b0\fs12}you are the best of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心靈最純潔\N{\b0\fs12}You have the purest heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讓你失去那份純潔\N{\b0\fs12}And I can't ever have you lose that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,答應我\N{\b0\fs12}You promise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道自己並非一直都是好哥哥\N{\b0\fs12}I know that I haven't always been the best brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或是朋友  或是別的什麼你所期望的\N{\b0\fs12}or friend, or whatever you've needed me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是自從你出生以來的每一天\N{\b0\fs12}But there has not been a day since you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我都因為有你這樣一個妹妹而倍感珍惜\N{\b0\fs12}where I didn't cherish having you as a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\b0\fs12}I'll, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等我安頓下來會聯繫你的\N{\b0\fs12}get in touch when I get settled somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}呼叫伊莎貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It's Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現在結束一切吧\N{\b0\fs12}This ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一個人去碼頭\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be at the pier, I'll be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\b0\fs12}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得  你會死的\N{\b0\fs12}Peter, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經死了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,輻射中毒\N{\b0\fs12}Radiation poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃的小禮物\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo's little gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他想知道米拉庫魯是不是能治癒癌症\N{\b0\fs12}He said he needed to find out if Mirakuru could cure cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,估計我們永遠也不會知道了\N{\b0\fs12}Guess we'll never find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  彼得  我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I'm sorry, Peter, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃說英雄主義的本質就是為他人犧牲\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo said the essence of heroism is to die so that others can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直堅信這一點\N{\b0\fs12}I held on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是唯一能給我希望的事\N{\b0\fs12}It's the only thing that gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我決定去\N{\b0\fs12}So I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我無法拯救數百萬的性命\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, I may not be saving millions of lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能救你們\N{\b0\fs12}but I'll be saving yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是一切開始的地方\N{\b0\fs12}This is where it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那裡登上了"金牌奎恩"\N{\b0\fs12}Got on the "Queen's Gambit" right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該死在那艘船上\N{\b0\fs12}I should have died on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我死了  這一切都不會發生\N{\b0\fs12}If I had, none of this would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我永遠也不會遇到你\N{\b0\fs12}I never would have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵和我母親還會活著\N{\b0\fs12}Shado and my mother would still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人也不會因為我而死\N{\b0\fs12}No one else is going to die because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  搞什麼鬼\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.41,0:24:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.02,0:24:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你的身份告訴我了\N{\b0\fs12}He told me who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.32,0:24:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他傷害你了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did he hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他想傷害你\N{\b0\fs12}He was trying to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.20,0:24:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你失蹤之後\N{\b0\fs12}And when you went missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.69,0:24:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就聯繫了\N{\b0\fs12}I reached out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的搭檔們\N{\b0\fs12}to your partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他們告訴了我你的打算\N{\b0\fs12}They told me what you were planning on doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須那麼做\N{\b0\fs12}It's what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:24:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我們單獨談會兒嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Will you give us a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那個計劃實施的那天晚上\N{\b0\fs12}You thought about telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你就想告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}the night of the undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.77,0:25:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎每天晚上我都想告訴你\N{\b0\fs12}I thought about telling you almost every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼不說\N{\b0\fs12}Why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.13,0:25:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,湯米知道\N{\b0\fs12}Tommy knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你當時和他在一起\N{\b0\fs12}You were with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他臨死時你陪著他\N{\b0\fs12}You were with him at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.06,0:25:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他最後的話都是在掛念你\N{\b0\fs12}His last words were about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.43,0:25:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他想知道你是否安全\N{\b0\fs12}He wanted to know if you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我沒能救下他\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.58,0:25:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還有我母親\N{\b0\fs12}And my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.49,0:25:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還能救你\N{\b0\fs12}But I can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還能救西婭\N{\b0\fs12}And Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.63,0:25:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我今晚了結這一切  我還能救下星城\N{\b0\fs12}I can save the city if this ends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.20,0:25:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不對\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能白白送死  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}You can't commit suicide, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能對我這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}You won't do that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還有莎拉  還有你的朋友們\N{\b0\fs12}Or to Sara, or to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.41,0:26:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還有西婭  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Or to Thea. Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她剛剛失去母親\N{\b0\fs12}She just lost her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再失去你就會徹底毀了她\N{\b0\fs12}Losing you would destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.43,0:26:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但她至少能活著\N{\b0\fs12}But she'll be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.50,0:26:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我對兜帽或者面具或者人造武器\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know anything about hoods and masks or human weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.22,0:26:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,或這裡的一切並不瞭解\N{\b0\fs12}or any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.03,0:26:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我瞭解你\N{\b0\fs12}But I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像熟知自己的名字那樣瞭解你\N{\b0\fs12}I know you like I know my own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,鑒於你的種種秘密  我知道這麼想很瘋狂\N{\b0\fs12}And I realize it may sound crazy in light of your secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.18,0:26:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我對你的為人和品行瞭若指掌  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}but I know who you are in your bones, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.39,0:26:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而我認識的這個人\N{\b0\fs12}And that person--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.28,0:26:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人從不輕言放棄\N{\b0\fs12}That person doesn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.51,0:26:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人總能另辟蹊徑\N{\b0\fs12}That person, he always finds a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.77,0:26:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這次不行了\N{\b0\fs12}Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.04,0:26:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你錯了\N{\b0\fs12}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.40,0:26:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想保護你深愛的人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You want to protect the people who you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.53,0:26:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就必須阻止斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}Then the only way to do that is to stop Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.96,0:26:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-勞蕾爾  我做不到  -你當然能\N{\b0\fs12}- Laurel, I can't! - Yes, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.15,0:27:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要阻止塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德  因為他\N{\b0\fs12}By stopping Sebastian Blood, because Sebastian
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.29,0:27:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正在和斯萊德•威爾遜合謀\N{\b0\fs12}is working with Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.52,0:27:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我有證據\N{\b0\fs12}I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜殺死你的母親\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson killed your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.86,0:27:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了把塞巴斯蒂安推上市長大位\N{\b0\fs12}so that Sebastian could become mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.11,0:27:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前說的他的事全是對的\N{\b0\fs12}You were right about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,戴骷髏面具的人為斯萊德•威爾遜工作\N{\b0\fs12}The man in the skull mask works for Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.96,0:27:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而一直以來\N{\b0\fs12}And this entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.23,0:27:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人就是塞巴斯蒂安\N{\b0\fs12}it was Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,當下的情勢\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.49,0:27:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已經遠超你和斯萊德的私怨了\N{\b0\fs12}is bigger than you and Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.99,0:27:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,星城需要綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}This city needs the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.48,0:28:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.61,0:28:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能避一避\N{\b0\fs12}I don't want you to be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.22,0:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  我要和你在一起  -莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}- No, I'm going to stay with you-- - Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.96,0:28:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果計劃失敗了\N{\b0\fs12}If this doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.03,0:28:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要確保你的安全\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.38,0:28:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,事成之後我們就去找你\N{\b0\fs12}We will come for you when it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.22,0:28:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\b0\fs12}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.15,0:28:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄清楚怎麼發射魚雷了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you know how the torpedo works?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.74,0:28:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我爬進去  他發射  我操縱  你祈禱\N{\b0\fs12}I get in, he fires, I steer, you pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.27,0:28:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得  你的這種行為實在是\N{\b0\fs12}Peter, what you're doing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.76,0:28:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看清現實而已\N{\b0\fs12}Practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經壽命將盡\N{\b0\fs12}My time's already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.57,0:28:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想說勇敢\N{\b0\fs12}Brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.98,0:28:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須知道這點\N{\b0\fs12}You need to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.14,0:28:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我就沒法像你這樣犧牲自我\N{\b0\fs12}And I don't think that I could do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.10,0:28:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經做到了  看看你為我們做的種種\N{\b0\fs12}You have. What you did for us--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.75,0:28:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,殺回船上  救出我們\N{\b0\fs12}coming back to that boat, setting us free?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.20,0:28:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我回到船上是因為我想回家\N{\b0\fs12}I came back to the boat because I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.04,0:28:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我本無意拯救任何人\N{\b0\fs12}I wasn't thinking about saving anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.17,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不是這樣的人\N{\b0\fs12}It's...it's not who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.29,0:28:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,或許現在還不是\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.80,0:29:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-發射嗎  -莎拉安全了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}- Launch? - Is Sara clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.24,0:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-安全了  -那就動手\N{\b0\fs12}- Yes. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-您好  -幸會\N{\b0\fs12}- Hello. - Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.66,0:29:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,克林頓  你在車裡等我吧\N{\b0\fs12}Clinton. You can wait in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.62,0:29:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您確定這樣沒問題嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you sure that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.28,0:29:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會有事的\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing's going to happen to me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.77,0:29:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您好啊  市長先生\N{\b0\fs12}How are you doing, mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.66,0:30:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,您好  幸會  很高興見到您\N{\b0\fs12}Hi. Good to see you, good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.44,0:30:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-您好  謝謝  -謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}- Hey, thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.04,0:30:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-您好  -很榮幸見到您  市長\N{\b0\fs12}- Hi. - Good to see you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.92,0:30:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜您  布拉德市長\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations, Mayor Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.84,0:30:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,幸會幸會\N{\b0\fs12}Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.94,0:30:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安  能一起吃頓飯嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sebastian, may I join you for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.93,0:30:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩等一下\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, can you hold that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太感謝了  哥們  太感謝了\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, thanks a lot, man, appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.09,0:30:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克林頓•霍格\N{\b0\fs12}Clinton Hogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.88,0:30:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些問題要問你\N{\b0\fs12}I have some questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.96,0:30:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧你們\N{\b0\fs12}Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.95,0:30:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定要這麼硬撐著嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You sure that's how you want to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我之前沒挨過打嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You think I've never took a beating before?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.41,0:30:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄  到最後你會寧可挨打\N{\b0\fs12}Pal, you're going to wish I beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.06,0:30:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我來審問你\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be your interrogator.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.75,0:31:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-逗我呢  -克林頓•霍格\N{\b0\fs12}- Is this a joke? - Clinton Hogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.35,0:31:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,社會保障號碼為306003894\N{\b0\fs12}Social security number 306003894.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.65,0:31:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們想幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell's this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.30,0:31:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.22,0:31:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在開曼群島還有個銀行帳戶呢\N{\b0\fs12}You have a bank account in the Cayman Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.26,0:31:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兩百萬  小金庫挺充實啊\N{\b0\fs12}$2 million, quite the little nest egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.44,0:31:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  貌似你剛剛\N{\b0\fs12}But...looks like you just
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.69,0:31:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,進行了一筆轉賬\N{\b0\fs12}approved a wire transfer of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.85,0:31:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把一百萬電匯進星城的一家慈善機構了\N{\b0\fs12}$1 million to a charity here in Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.89,0:31:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真是慷慨啊\N{\b0\fs12}Very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.02,0:31:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的該怎麼辦呢\N{\b0\fs12}What should I do with the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.09,0:31:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-綠色和平[環保組織]  -好主意\N{\b0\fs12}- Greenpeace. - Great cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.97,0:31:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他們非常感謝你的傾囊相助\N{\b0\fs12}And they really appreciate the support.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.17,0:31:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你個婊子\N{\b0\fs12}You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.28,0:31:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能上無線網的婊子\N{\b0\fs12}Bitch with wifi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.63,0:31:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,克林頓  看來你父母的\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, Clinton, looks like your mom and dad have
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.21,0:31:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,退休金投資收益頗豐啊\N{\b0\fs12}a really nice retirement portfolio, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.10,0:31:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是糟了  他們馬上\N{\b0\fs12}but they, oh, no, are just
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.64,0:31:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就要做一筆血賠的投資了\N{\b0\fs12}about to make some really bad investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.08,0:31:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著  別  停下\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, wait, just wait--just--stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.24,0:31:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你們想知道什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你母親的追悼會上沒見著你\N{\b0\fs12}I missed you at your mother's memorial service.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.33,0:31:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想當面表達哀悼之情的\N{\b0\fs12}I wanted to offer my condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.94,0:32:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你當上市長了\N{\b0\fs12}You're the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.08,0:32:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜了\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你奮鬥多年的夢想\N{\b0\fs12}You've always wanted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我奧利弗  我更希望換種方式上任\N{\b0\fs12}Believe me, Oliver, I wish it had happened a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.72,0:32:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,令堂和我  我們政見相差甚遠\N{\b0\fs12}Your mother and I, we--we didn't agree on much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.49,0:32:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們都是為星城著想\N{\b0\fs12}But we both wanted what was best for Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.70,0:32:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫這座城市重尋希望  我向你保證\N{\b0\fs12}I will help this city find its heart again, I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.54,0:32:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你真覺得他...\N{\b0\fs12}Do you really think that he...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.36,0:32:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,會讓你這麼做嗎\N{\b0\fs12}will let that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.71,0:32:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我跟斯萊德•威爾遜的事\N{\b0\fs12}How do you know I've been working with Slade Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.11,0:32:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我就是綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}Because I'm the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.25,0:32:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得啊\N{\b0\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.61,0:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我都明白了\N{\b0\fs12}It all makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.62,0:32:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭俠原來就在我身邊\N{\b0\fs12}It was right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.25,0:33:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你到我辦公室跟我握手\N{\b0\fs12}You came to my office and you shook my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.69,0:33:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你說我們一起拯救星城\N{\b0\fs12}You said that together, we can save this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.75,0:33:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得你釋放斯萊德的米拉庫魯大軍後\N{\b0\fs12}You think that there will be a city to be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.42,0:33:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還有城市可以拯救嗎\N{\b0\fs12}after you unleash Slade's Mirakuru army?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.87,0:33:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們導致的損失  只是讓星城做好準備\N{\b0\fs12}They'll only cause enough damage to make the city ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.76,0:33:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,準備接受你的領導嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Ready for your leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.63,0:33:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,準備實現我對這個城市的遠大期望\N{\b0\fs12}For my vision of what this city could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,變成更好的城市\N{\b0\fs12}A better city.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.42,0:33:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,經歷過暴風雨般的洗禮之後\N{\b0\fs12}And after the storm they're about to suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.43,0:33:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,星城人民\N{\b0\fs12}the people of Starling
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.45,0:33:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,會支持並跟隨我去建造那座城市\N{\b0\fs12}will support and follow me to that city.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.89,0:33:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德承諾你的絕對不會兌現\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever Slade promised you, he will not deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.17,0:33:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是想傷害我\N{\b0\fs12}He wants to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.31,0:33:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是一盤更大的棋局裡的棋子\N{\b0\fs12}You are a pawn in a much larger game.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.87,0:33:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德承諾讓我當市長\N{\b0\fs12}Slade promised me city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.84,0:33:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他兌現了這個承諾\N{\b0\fs12}And he delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.63,0:33:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他挺言而有信的\N{\b0\fs12}He makes good on his promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.39,0:33:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他也向你作出過承諾\N{\b0\fs12}I understand he made you a promise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.09,0:34:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.39,0:34:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在大庭廣眾的餐廳裡\N{\b0\fs12}You going to stab the mayor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.42,0:34:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,刺殺市長嗎\N{\b0\fs12}in a restaurant full of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.95,0:34:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,星城的歷史翻開了新篇章  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It's a new day in Starling City, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.63,0:34:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,無論你做什麼  都無法阻擋歷史的腳步\N{\b0\fs12}And there's nothing you can do to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.48,0:34:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}沃爾特來電
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:35:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}沃爾特來電  拒絕接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.12,0:35:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德的人今晚要發起進攻\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's men are taking the city tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.23,0:35:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-讓他們試試吧  -人數比我們想像的要多\N{\b0\fs12}- They can try. - There's more men than we thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.95,0:35:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都服用了米拉庫魯  可能是場屠殺\N{\b0\fs12}all on Mirakuru. It could be a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.24,0:35:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我們先下手為強\N{\b0\fs12}Not if we get to them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何  我們按原定計劃行事\N{\b0\fs12}We stick to the plan, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.46,0:35:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德會利用下水道系統\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's using the sewer system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.37,0:35:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可以從洛克街過去  然後往東南走\N{\b0\fs12}You can drop in at Rock Avenue and then head southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.23,0:35:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,管線匯集處在沃特街\N{\b0\fs12}The lines converge at Water Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.18,0:35:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果斯萊德的大軍在地下  他可能就在那裡\N{\b0\fs12}If Slade's army's underground, that's probably where he'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.15,0:35:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我們走  狄格爾  準備好了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Good. Let's go. Diggle, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然\N{\b0\fs12}Never not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.97,0:35:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要一起去\N{\b0\fs12}I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.84,0:35:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs12}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.98,0:35:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂可以把消息給我\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity can give me a radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.07,0:35:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以時刻告訴你們最新情況\N{\b0\fs12}I'll just be your eyes and your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.59,0:35:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會礙事的  我保證\N{\b0\fs12}I'll stay out of your way, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.42,0:35:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不會有事的  -萬一出事了呢\N{\b0\fs12}- Nothing will happen to me. - What if it did?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.47,0:35:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德的人個個都能力強大  幾乎無法阻止\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's men, one on one, they are nearly impossible to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.62,0:36:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你相信我\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.01,0:36:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你好好的\N{\b0\fs12}And I need you to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.39,0:36:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那他們兩個呢\N{\b0\fs12}But not them?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.32,0:36:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事開始就是我們三個人一起做的\N{\b0\fs12}This started with the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.92,0:36:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候回到最初的陣容了\N{\b0\fs12}It's time we got back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.27,0:37:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我們齊心協力\N{\b0\fs12}Tonight we rise up as one
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.33,0:37:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,奪回這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}and take back this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.33,0:37:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到布拉德的大軍了\N{\b0\fs12}I have eyes on Blood's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  我馬上把\N{\b0\fs12}Got it. I'm forwarding dig your ping
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.38,0:37:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們上面街道的設計圖轉發到你手機上\N{\b0\fs12}along with the foundation schematics of the topside avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.01,0:37:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,按照我給你畫出的路線走\N{\b0\fs12}Follow the route I laid out on the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.64,0:37:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會看到結構內部的接合點了\N{\b0\fs12}You'll see structural joints in the concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下載中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.69,0:37:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.79,0:37:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,都炸掉  布拉德就葬身地下了\N{\b0\fs12}Blow them all and Blood gets buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\b0\fs12}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.18,0:37:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天股市以400點開市\N{\b0\fs12}The market opened today at 400 points
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.42,0:37:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,部分原因是奎恩聯合企業的突然奮起\N{\b0\fs12}thanks in part to the surprise rally of Queen's Consolidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.91,0:37:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,盡管最近發生了悲劇  但是新領導班子\N{\b0\fs12}New leadership has investers excited about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.07,0:37:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讓投資者對公司的前景大為看好\N{\b0\fs12}...the company's future in spite of this recent tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.41,0:37:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請問一下  為什麼現在還不能上車\N{\b0\fs12}Um, excuse me, why can't I board my train?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.70,0:37:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  女士  現在是商務座旅客上車時間\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, ma'am, it's just business class right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,普座稍後就可以了\N{\b0\fs12}Coach will be boarding soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.14,0:38:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.51,0:38:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,過來  夥計\N{\b0\fs12}Come on, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.85,0:38:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是鐵山監獄的逃犯嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Isn't that one of the Iron Heights escapees?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.83,0:38:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個笨蛋想去搶便利店\N{\b0\fs12}Dumbass here tried to rob a convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.65,0:38:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我過去他就束手就擒了\N{\b0\fs12}but gave up as soon as I pulled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.35,0:38:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以暫時把他留在這裡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Mind if I just stick him here for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.65,0:38:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\b0\fs12}No, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.40,0:38:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你說\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just asking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.56,0:38:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你一直那麼努力去避免再殺人\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, you've worked really hard not to kill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.84,0:38:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把整個街區炸毀埋了那些人無異於謀殺\N{\b0\fs12}Dropping an entire block on these guys is murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.61,0:38:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,至少是屠殺\N{\b0\fs12}Manslaughter, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.60,0:38:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是人\N{\b0\fs12}They're not men.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.07,0:38:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不是了\N{\b0\fs12}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.94,0:38:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾一準備好就讓他引爆炸藥\N{\b0\fs12}Have Diggle blow the charges the moment he's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.79,0:38:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將帶領這座城市走出黑暗\N{\b0\fs12}We will lead this city out of the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.39,0:38:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都將助我一臂之力\N{\b0\fs12}and each one of you will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\b0\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.68,0:39:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你到底在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, where the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.78,0:39:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你殺了我...\N{\b0\fs12}You killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.03,0:39:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那就禮尚往來吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let me return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.84,0:40:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,現在幾點了\N{\b0\fs12}You got the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.32,0:40:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,九點\N{\b0\fs12}It's, uh, 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.92,0:40:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  快出現\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.66,0:40:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星級實驗室來電
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.34,0:40:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,西斯科  現在真不是時候\N{\b0\fs12}Cisco, now is really not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.45,0:40:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊\N{\b0\fs12}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.10,0:41:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.91,0:41:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他們人太多了\N{\b0\fs12}There's too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.53,0:41:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們打不過\N{\b0\fs12}We can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不跟他們打\N{\b0\fs12}We're not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.92,0:41:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,轉舵\N{\b0\fs12}Turn the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.79,0:41:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,往哪個方向\N{\b0\fs12}What direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.64,0:41:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂  快轉舵\N{\b0\fs12}It does not matter. Just turn the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.50,0:41:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-轉不動  -必須轉\N{\b0\fs12}- I can't! - That is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.54,0:41:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\b0\fs12}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.39,0:41:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶  動了\N{\b0\fs12}My God. We're moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.37,0:41:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好  太棒了\N{\b0\fs12}Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.46,0:41:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  成功了\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.09,0:41:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.22,0:41:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
